<plot>"Flushed" is a short tragi-comic tone poem, set in the washroom of a small and relatively decrepit art-house cinema. Within its walls, three isolated and lonely individuals - Shane, Anna and Boris- will try, unsuccessfully, to forge some sort of connection between on another, and their plight shall be 'witnessed' by the bathroom's attendant - an attendant who is completely deaf, mute and blind.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?198432</url></doc>
